paper_title: Temperature-dependent discovery of BCC refractory multi-principal element alloys: Integrating deep learning and CALPHAD calculations

claims.claim: The trained random forest model identifies the top five features ranked by importance as PFP_BCC, Delta, T, PFP_FCC, and Etha
instruction: The code trains the random forest using the training dataset, obtains the feature importance ranking, and prints the top 5 features.
Verify that the printed top 5 features are: ["$PFP_{\\mathrm{BCC}}$", "$\\delta$", "$T$", "$PFP_{\\mathrm{FCC}}$", "$\\eta$"]
